Steps:

1) Download the admin template https://www.microsoft.com/edge/business/download
2) Modify the group POlicy Object Editor 
3) allow the user to input the sharepoint domain
4) group Policy update
#
https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/deployedge/microsoft-edge-policies#configureviewinfileexplorer
SOFTWARE\Policies\Microsoft\Edge\ConfigureViewInFileExplorer = [{"cookies": ["rtFa", "FedAuth"], "domain": "contoso.sharepoint.com"}, {"cookies": ["rtFa", "FedAuth"], "domain": "contoso2.sharepoint.com"}]
